On Monday April 6th, I placed an order online with this store for $120.00, Nevermind that they were overpriced, but they never even bothered to deliver the order. I reached out to them on the Tuesday the 7th and they told me that they cancelled the order the previous night. THEY DIDN'T EVEN BOTHER TO REACH OUT TO ME TO TELL ME, THAT THEY CANCELLED THE ORDER. While I can understand that they cancelled the order, I can't under why they wouldn't even call to let me know that they did that. And that 15hrs later I have to call to find out. To make matters worse THEY WOULDN'T EVEN ISSUE A REFUND, or even offer to make the order as they were too busy. So essentially to boil the story down, they took $120.00 from me and the refused to give me my food or my money back. I would avoid this place like the plague.
